msgid "# Set-DnsServerRecursion"
msgstr "# Set-DnsServerRecursion"

msgid "## SYNOPSIS"
msgstr "## 概要"

msgid "Modifies recursion settings for a DNS server."
msgstr "修改DNS服务器的递归设置。"

msgid "## SYNTAX"
msgstr "## 语法"

msgid "## DESCRIPTION"
msgstr "## 说明"

msgid ""
"The **Set-DnsServerRecursion** cmdlet modifies recursion settings for a Domain Name System (DNS) server.\n"
"Recursion occurs when a DNS server queries other DNS servers on behalf of a requesting client, and then sends the answer back to the client."
msgstr ""
"`Set-DnsServerRecursion` cmdlet 用于修改域名系统（DNS）服务器的递归设置。当 DNS 服务器代表请求客户端向其他 "
"DNS 服务器发起查询，并将查询结果返回给客户端时，就发生了递归过程。"

msgid "## EXAMPLES"
msgstr "## 示例"

msgid "### Example 1: Set the retry interval"
msgstr "### 示例 1：设置重试间隔"

msgid "This command sets the retry interval to 15 seconds."
msgstr "这个命令将重试间隔设置为15秒。"

msgid "## PARAMETERS"
msgstr "## 参数"

msgid ""
"Specifies the time interval, in seconds, that a DNS server waits as it uses recursion to get resource records from a remote DNS server.\n"
"We recommend that you limit the value to the range 0x00000000 to 0x0000000F (0 seconds to 15 seconds), inclusive.\n"
"However, you can use any value.\n"
"We recommend that you set the default value to 4."
msgstr ""
"指定 DNS 服务器在使用递归从远程 DNS 服务器获取资源记录时所等待的时间间隔（以秒为单位）。建议将此值限制在 0x00000000 到 "
"0x0000000F 的范围内（即 0 秒到 15 秒，包括两端值）。不过，您也可以使用任何其他数值。默认情况下，我们建议将该值设置为 4。"

msgid ""
"Runs the cmdlet as a background job. Use this parameter to run commands that"
" take a long time to complete."
msgstr "将此cmdlet作为后台作业运行。使用此参数来执行需要很长时间才能完成的命令。"

msgid ""
"The cmdlet immediately returns an object that represents the job and then displays the command prompt.\n"
"You can continue to work in the session while the job completes.\n"
"To manage the job, use the `*-Job` cmdlets.\n"
"To get the job results, use the [Receive-Job](https://go.microsoft.com/fwlink/?LinkID=113372) cmdlet."
msgstr ""
"该cmdlet会立即返回一个表示作业的对象，然后显示命令提示符。在作业完成之前，您可以继续在该会话中工作。要管理作业，请使用`*-Job`系列的cmdlets；要获取作业结果，请使用[Receive-"
"Job](https://go.microsoft.com/fwlink/?LinkID=113372) cmdlet。"

msgid ""
"For more information about Windows PowerShell background jobs, see "
"[about_Jobs](https://go.microsoft.com/fwlink/?LinkID=113251)."
msgstr ""
"有关 Windows PowerShell 后台作业的更多信息，请参阅 [关于作业（About "
"Jobs）](https://go.microsoft.com/fwlink/?LinkID=113251)。"

msgid ""
"Runs the cmdlet in a remote session or on a remote computer.\n"
"Enter a computer name or a session object, such as the output of a [New-CimSession](https://go.microsoft.com/fwlink/p/?LinkId=227967) or [Get-CimSession](https://go.microsoft.com/fwlink/p/?LinkId=227966) cmdlet.\n"
"The default is the current session on the local computer."
msgstr ""
"在远程会话或远程计算机上运行该 cmdlet。可以输入一个计算机名称，或者提供一个会话对象（例如 [New-"
"CimSession](https://go.microsoft.com/fwlink/p/?LinkId=227967) 或 [Get-"
"CimSession](https://go.microsoft.com/fwlink/p/?LinkId=227966) cmdlet "
"的输出结果）。默认值是本地计算机上的当前会话。"

msgid ""
"Specifies a DNS server.\n"
"The acceptable values for this parameter are: an IPv4 address; an IPv6 address; and any other value that resolves to an IP address, such as a fully qualified domain name (FQDN), host name, or NETBIOS name."
msgstr ""
"用于指定一个DNS服务器。该参数的可接受值包括：IPv4地址；IPv6地址；以及任何能够解析为IP地址的其他值，例如完全限定域名（FQDN）、主机名或NETBIOS名称。"

msgid "Prompts you for confirmation before running the cmdlet."
msgstr "在运行该cmdlet之前，会提示您确认是否要执行该操作。"

msgid "Specifies whether the server enables recursion."
msgstr "指定服务器是否支持递归功能。"

msgid ""
"Returns an object representing the item with which you are working.\n"
"By default, this cmdlet does not generate any output."
msgstr "返回一个表示您正在操作的项目的对象。默认情况下，此 cmdlet 不会生成任何输出。"

msgid ""
"Specifies elapsed seconds before a DNS server retries a recursive lookup.\n"
"If the parameter is undefined or zero, the DNS server retries after three seconds.\n"
"Valid values are in the range of 1 second to 15 seconds."
msgstr ""
"该参数指定DNS服务器在重试递归查询之前等待的秒数。如果该参数未定义或设置为0，则DNS服务器将在3秒后重试。有效取值范围为1秒到15秒之间。"

msgid ""
"We recommend that in general, you do not change the value of this parameter.\n"
"However, under a few circumstances you should consider changing the parameter value.\n"
"For example, if a DNS server contacts a remote DNS server over a slow link and retries the lookup before it gets a response, you can raise the retry interval to be slightly longer than the observed response time."
msgstr ""
"我们建议一般情况下不要更改该参数的值。但在某些情况下，您应该考虑修改该参数的值。例如，如果一个DNS服务器通过速度较慢的链接与远程DNS服务器进行通信，并在收到响应之前重复尝试查询，那么您可以将重试间隔设置得稍长于实际观察到的响应时间。"

msgid ""
"Indicates whether a DNS server screens DNS records against the zone of authority for the remote server, to prevent cache pollution.\n"
"If you set this to $True, the DNS server caches only those records that are in the zone of authority for the queried remote server.\n"
"Otherwise, the server caches all records in the remote server cache."
msgstr ""
"该选项用于指示DNS服务器是否会根据远程服务器的权威区域来筛选DNS记录，以防止缓存污染。如果将此值设置为$True，DNS服务器只会缓存属于所查询远程服务器权威区域的记录；否则，服务器会缓存远程服务器缓存中的所有记录。"

msgid ""
"Specifies the maximum number of concurrent operations that can be established to run the cmdlet.\n"
"If this parameter is omitted or a value of `0` is entered, then Windows PowerShell® calculates an optimum throttle limit for the cmdlet based on the number of CIM cmdlets that are running on the computer.\n"
"The throttle limit applies only to the current cmdlet, not to the session or to the computer."
msgstr ""
"该参数用于指定可以同时运行的 cmdlet 操作的最大数量。如果省略此参数或输入值 `0`，Windows PowerShell® "
"会根据计算机上正在运行的 CIM cmdlet 的数量来计算该 cmdlet 的最佳限制值。此限制仅适用于当前运行的 "
"cmdlet，而不适用于整个会话或计算机本身。"

msgid ""
"Specifies the number of seconds that a DNS server waits before it stops trying to contact a remote server.\n"
"The valid value is in the range of 0x1 to 0xFFFFFFFF (1 second to 15 seconds).\n"
"The default setting is 0x8 (8 seconds).\n"
"We recommend that you increase this value when recursion occurs over a slow link."
msgstr ""
"指定 DNS 服务器在停止尝试联系远程服务器之前等待的秒数。有效值的范围是 0x1 到 0xFFFFFFFF（1 秒到 15 秒）。默认设置为 "
"0x8（8 秒）。我们建议在通过较慢的网络链接进行递归查询时增加此值。"

msgid ""
"Shows what would happen if the cmdlet runs.\n"
"The cmdlet is not run."
msgstr "展示了如果运行该cmdlet会发生什么情况。但实际上该cmdlet并没有被执行。"

